1","tid":613752,"uid":77788,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e97a6c3f8183434f173396b87ecdcfdc6149f24","tid":613752,"uid":28734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"109536800e20e29a3a8563da344a941ec1b82471","tid":613752,"uid":77788,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"強國救世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e605c79fa92b6926a8da245ae55ce34d092e4448","tid":613752,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfdd7170437bdc99968e0391d4c4332bdef4d91","tid":613752,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5e97a6c3f8183434f173396b87ecdcfdc6149f24","tid":613752,"uid":28734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"109536800e20e29a3a8563da344a941ec1b82471","tid":613752,"uid":77788,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"強國救世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8f3a950839479fec456903236598f88475fac6","tid":613752,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"支那飛機片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180ccf77d576395b2ea828672256d0be2650e093","tid":613752,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7f8f3a950839479fec456903236598f88475fac6","tid":613752,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"支那飛機片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"《The China Hustle》唔係強國飛機片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.weibo.cn/status/4223767485897321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4223767485897321&d=hk8iL1Q5AFeEi9VmpvWFnjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f4ed54b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.weibo.cn/status/4223767485897321</a><br />\n<br />\nvv927<br />\n我还以为中国公司只在国内割韭菜，没想到全球一盘棋啊[笑cry][笑cry]<br />\n<br />\nV柏青哥V2<br />\n只有你们不敢想，没有他们不敢做[摊手]<br />\n<br />\nzz的微博号<br />\n呵呵，黑中国？中国只有更黑，善良的美国佬根本想象不到。还有一点非常搞不懂的是，中国的企业，国内都知道是垃圾，为啥能纷纷跑到美国上市呢？<br />\n<br />\n徒步喀拉斯湖<br />\n中国股市就是骗子公司！上市就是为了圈钱、弄到钱就跑了！等股民接盘、太吓人<br />\n<br />\ncolorful-days<br />\n有什么样的政府，就有什么样的企业。这叫上梁不正下梁歪。现在为了保国家的外储、中国政府也是拼了，让有资格的公司去美国上市、把融资到的美元拿回国内填补外汇缺口。让在美国上市的中资公司退市、回国内上市。把退市的美元拿回国内填补国内外汇缺口。可想而知，中国外储以告急。<br />\n<br />\n安希斯Ansis<br />\n连万恶的美帝都能骗到，体现了社会主义的优越性。<br />\n<br />\n萧淳元<br />\n赴美IPO创业者川粉居多，原因很简单，大家行骗的对象都是美国半文盲。川普的成功可以在股票市场上复制。<br />\n<br />\n无业市民911<br />\n我一个朋友曾经在一家在纳斯达克上市的中国的公司的一家分厂当厂长。该公司主要是回收饭店的泔水然后加工成燃料油，说到如何造假，每天都有十几台的运泔水的空车在跑，以欺骗来厂考察的美市场分析师以及美投资者。"},{"pid":"e41cdc949a16daf625032d0a8053dbaffcae88b5","tid":613752,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e276da5b1da383a1101e5cb0d82e310a031972a","tid":613752,"uid":28588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:47:36.000Z","msg":"根本股票市場就係一個騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c0f46e26379e9b8def3f162977eac4a35cfd8c","tid":613752,"uid":5463,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e276da5b1da383a1101e5cb0d82e310a031972a","tid":613752,"uid":28588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:47:36.000Z","msg":"根本股票市場就係一個騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:05:53.000Z","msg"